+    </td>
+    <td style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #333;">
+      <b>RUST BACKEND</b><br>
+      A memory-safe backend that handles all file operations and game execution with minimal overhead.
+    </td>
+  </tr>
+  <tr>
+    <td style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #333;">
+      <b>EASY CONFIGURATION</b><br>
